steps.name: Given there is user Alice in Ethereum network with the initial balance 100Ξ
And there is user Bob in Ethereum network with the initial balance 100Ξ
When user Alice sends 20Ξ to user Bob
Then the recipient has balance increased by 20Ξ
And the sender has balance decreased more than by 20Ξ
